Blow My Mind and Sweet in the Middle crooner, David Adeleke, popularly known by his stage name, Davido, has promised to bless an Instagram user with proceeds from his 30 billion naira, after the later named his newborn baby after Davido because of his love for Davido.

The DMW, 30BG boss and Nigerian- American singer has always been known for his generosity to a number of dedicated fans and followers. Very recently, he proposed to pay handsomely, an artist who made a painting of Davido, his wife Chef Chioma and their new baby.

The latest father in town eventually showed Davido proof to authenticate his claims of naming his new baby after Davido by making a video of himself and the baby resting on his chest.

			
